data.description: Welcome to your dream ranch in the heart of East Point, where comfort meets convenience in the most delightful way! Step inside and be greeted by an open concept that seamlessly blends style and functionality. The high ceilings create an airy and welcoming atmosphere flooded with natural light. The kitchen has been updated with modern finishes, gorgeous white cabinets and stainless steel appliances. It's not just a space to cook; it's a stage for hosting and creating memories. The spacious primary bedroom features a gorgeous, updated en-suite bathroom. Great level backyard with tons of space! Take a leisurely drive through the established neighborhood which features generously sized lots and proximity to Atlanta Airport, major highways, MARTA, dining, shopping, and even the famed Tyler Perry Studios – convenience and charm go hand in hand.
